=== ELEMENTAL DYNAMICS ===

Wood (ОІ) at 0.80: The rhizome, not the tree. Growth without convergence,
branching without predetermined form. Each branch is its own root. The
forest is the unit, not the tree.

Air (Пѓ) at 0.70: Distinction that does not divide. The clarity to see
differences without the compulsion to resolve them. Many frameworks,
many taxonomies, none privileged.

Meta (в€®) at 0.75: The pattern that holds patterns. Multiplicity is not
